- Pinned Maps SDK to `v=quarterly` in production (`v=weekly` in dev). Tree-shake-verified.
- Added `@googlemaps/markerclusterer ^2.6.2` — pins cluster at city zoom, fan out on zoom-in. `onClusterClick` emits telemetry.
- A11y on markers: `role="button"`, `aria-label`, `aria-current`, `aria-hidden` on emoji.
- `clearPins()` on conversation change — pins no longer bleed across conversations.

**ChatLeftNav + Search this area (Day 1 sprint):**
