**Critical bug fixes folded into the same PR:**
- `9b86f72` + `1be13e6` — `/apartments/:id`, `/cars/:id`, `/restaurants/:id` rendered blank because `usePanelContext()` shim used CommonJS `require()` (doesn't exist in Vite/ESM). Migrated all 3 detail pages to `useThreePanelContext` from `@/components/explore/ThreePanelLayout`. Deleted the broken shim.
- `c9ea238` + `1a82f97` — anon synthetic `conversation.id` was `\`anon-${sid}\``, breaking `messages.conversation_id` (uuid type) with 400s and triggering `CHANNEL_ERROR`/`TIMED_OUT` realtime loops. Now a pure UUID via `useAnonSession` (`crypto.randomUUID()` + strict UUID regex on localStorage). Realtime gate switched to `conversation.user_id === user.id`.
- `e00b872` — fixed double-script load + duplicate gmp-* custom-element registration via the singleton loader (above).
- `701fb01` — CORS preflight was missing `Access-Control-Allow-Methods` → browsers silently aborted POSTs. Added `POST, GET, OPTIONS` + `x-anon-session-id` to `Allow-Headers`.

### PR #3 — `f1de3c1` — Hero rewrite: full-width chat window
