## 2026-04-05 (Edge + rentals polish)

### Edge functions (Supabase)
- **`Deno.serve` everywhere** — removed `std/http` `serve` import from ai-chat, ai-router, ai-search, ai-trip-planner, google-directions, ai-optimize-route, ai-suggest-collections, rules-engine (aligns with Supabase / Deno 2 guidance)
- **Per-request CORS** — all browser-invoked handlers use `getCorsHeaders(req)` + `jsonResponse(..., req)` (or equivalent); **`OPTIONS` → 204** where updated; Vercel preview / localhost get correct `Access-Control-Allow-Origin` (not only static `mdeai.co`)
- **`requireCronSecret`** — 403 responses pass `req` into `jsonResponse` for CORS consistency
- **`ai-optimize-route`** — **`insertAiRun`** on Gemini success / upstream error / parse fallback when JWT user present; uses `_shared/supabase-clients` + `getCorsHeaders` + `okJson` helper

### `rentals` edge function
- **Backward-compatible API** — `preprocessRentalBody` maps legacy `user_message` + `context.message_history` → `messages[]`, `listing_id` → `id`; search response adds flat **`listings` / `total` / `map_pins` / `facets`** for older callers; intake adds **`status` / `summary`**; verify adds **`freshness_status`**; map pins accept numeric coords as **number or string** from PostgREST

### Frontend (P1 / apartments)
- **`ApartmentRentActions`** — idempotency key for tour + application **rotates in `useEffect` when dialog opens** (controlled Radix `Dialog` often does not call `onOpenChange(true)` on programmatic open — reused key caused silent server no-ops on second submit)

